    <item>
      <title>布林肯称俄罗斯正试图利用冬季对乌克兰发动攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/russia-is-trying-to-weaponize-winter-blinken-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，俄罗斯正试图通过集中攻击能源基础设施目标，将冬季“武器化”来对付乌克兰。他说，弗拉基米尔·普京正试图将人们冻得无法回家。他在北约总部发表了讲话，各国外长聚集在这里，讨论向乌克兰提供更多武器。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-06/russia-is-trying-to-weaponize-winter-blinken-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 13:16:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰利率委员会关系紧张，行长寻求推迟降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/polish-rate-panel-tensions-fray-as-governor-seeks-to-delay-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰政策制定者与央行行长亚当格拉宾斯基 (Adam Glapinski) 的观点保持距离，后者认为明年可能不会降息，这一分歧在该国经济放缓之际显现出来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/polish-rate-panel-tensions-fray-as-governor-seeks-to-delay-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 13:14:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟不顾法国反对，达成期待已久的南方共同市场协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/eu-reaches-long-sought-mercosur-deal-over-macron-s-objections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管法国强烈反对，欧盟与南美洲南方共同市场仍达成了一项期待已久的贸易协议，法国还誓言将带头阻挠该协议的批准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/eu-reaches-long-sought-mercosur-deal-over-macron-s-objections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 12:54:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称欧洲央行将对部分银行进行 SRT 买家杠杆率测试</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/ecb-is-said-to-quiz-some-banks-about-srt-buyers-use-of-leverage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行正在寻求弄清投资者如何利用借入的资金购买重大风险转移产品，以试图确保这种日益流行的结构有助于缓解风险敞口，而不是将其转移到整个银行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/ecb-is-said-to-quiz-some-banks-about-srt-buyers-use-of-leverage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 12:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国金融监督院称“增值”政策将经受住政治动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/korea-s-fss-chief-says-value-up-to-survive-political-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最高金融监管机构表示，由于韩国改善公司治理和提高股东回报的努力得到了两党的支持，这一举措将在政治动荡中得以延续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/korea-s-fss-chief-says-value-up-to-survive-political-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 08:15:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗集团因澳大利亚贸易失误损失逾 4,500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/citigroup-losses-reach-a-70-million-on-goodman-trade-afr-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，花旗集团因澳大利亚的一笔交易失误而蒙受的损失跃升至 7,000 多万澳元（4,500 万美元），这是近年来亚洲最大的大宗交易失误之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/citigroup-losses-reach-a-70-million-on-goodman-trade-afr-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:48:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OPEC+未能缓解供应担忧，油价跌至两周低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-6</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心 OPEC+ 推迟恢复停产的决定不会阻止明年形成过剩，油价跌至两周多以来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-05/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-6</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 23:25:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
